videos.description: Sarah Andrews scores eight points for Baylor in the first quarter vs. Oklahoma.

videos.headline: Sarah Andrews helps Baylor build 1st-quarter lead over Oklahoma

videos.description: Gabby Gregory misses a 3, but Oklahoma gets the ball back, and Madi Williams drives in to give the Sooners a 65-64 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Madi Williams' nice bucket gives Oklahoma the lead after 3) 2022/2/2 ESHEET

videos.headline: Madi Williams' nice bucket gives Oklahoma the lead after 3

videos.description: Sarah Andrews drives in for a nice finish while drawing a foul for Baylor.

videos.headline: Sarah Andrews' nifty bucket gives Baylor some insurance

videos.description: Liz Scott scores the go-ahead bucket with six seconds left, and Baylor can't score on its last possession as Oklahoma hangs on for a 78-77 win.
